author: Gabriel lzx
text:
One of the best Anytime Fitness gym branches in Singapore! All the gym equipment is the newest model and is brand new, and the washroom is more often in pristine condition.

The staff were wonderful too, especially Jeevan and Nia, as they were helpful and responsive through online inquiries, and showed great hospitality.

It is a gym worth signing up for the atmosphere, service, and ongoing promotions!

author: John S
text: Relatively small gym with limited equipment, especially for lower body. Lacking a seated leg curl, hacksquat or chest-supported rows. Only one smith machine while there‚Äôs 4-5 cardio machine. Good assortment of equipment for chest and arms, though.

author: Brunette L
text:
Great gym with well maintained equipments. Very well covered despite the size. However one thing for the management is that multiple times I've spotted gym go-ers not in proper shoes after hours. In slides etc

Update: please check your cctv 27/7/2025, around 9.30pm. 2 guys in crocs

author: Darshan Shan
text:
The facilities are top-notch, always clean and well-maintained. The equipment selection is vast and diverse, catering to all fitness levels.

But what truly sets the gym apart is the supportive community and exceptional staff. From friendly trainers to motivating group classes, everyone makes you feel welcome and encouraged.

author: Sharmila Jeyanthy
text: The facility is clean, well-maintained, and has all the equipment I need for a full workout. The staff are friendly and knowledgeable, and the environment is motivating. Whether you're a beginner or experienced, this gym has everything to help you reach your fitness goals!

author: Shaila Shehereen
text:
I recently joined Anytime Fitness Bukit batok connection and I couldn‚Äôt be happier with my experience! The atmosphere is welcoming and motivating, making it easy to stay committed to my fitness goals. The staff is incredibly friendly and knowledgeable, always ready to offer advice and support.

The variety of equipment is impressive. The trainers are fantastic, providing personalized guidance and encouragement that really helps push me to the next level.

Cleanliness is a top priority here, and I appreciate how well-maintained the facilities are. Plus, the community vibe is fantastic; I've met so many like-minded individuals who inspire me to keep coming back.

Overall, Anytime fitness bukit batok connection is the perfect place for anyone looking to enhance their fitness journey. Highly recommend!

author: sabrish ravi
text: Great gym with clean facilities, modern equipment, and friendly staffs. The trainers are knowledgeable, and the atmosphere is motivating. Perfect spot for both beginners and experienced fitness enthusiasts.

author: Gene Simmons
text: Hands down the cleanest and most comfortable Anytime Fitness I have worked out at and I have worked out at AFs across Singapore. Love the cosy vibes and the new machines, clean washroom. Plus it‚Äôs super close to where I live.
